            <div type="apparatus">
               <p>Pending</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>Saint Barbara</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Good condition. The writing of the beta is typical  throughout the Moutoullas monument but also in other churches in Cyprus of the end of the 13th century such as the church of the Transfiguration of the Saviour in Sotera Ammochostou. Probably the painter came from the same workshop. </p>
